 the Damage Trump Has Done in Latin America. Biden’s Plans Don’t Cut It.</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="326"><!-- react-text: 327 -->John Washington<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="328"><!-- react-text: 329 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 330 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="331">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="332"><!-- react-empty: 333 --></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="334"><div data-reactid="335"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="336"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/18/trump-urges-followers-risk-lives-rallies-wont-attend/" data-reactid="337"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="338"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="339"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="340"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="341"><noscript data-reactid="342"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/b2c9c56c-afe9-4ccc-8d4c-4397455ca432/b2c9c56c-afe9-4ccc-8d4c-4397455ca432.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=5da42725e1af7edf3c2cd744f22d72aa" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="343"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="344"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="345"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="346"><span class="Promo-title-wrap" data-reactid="347">If Trump Thinks It’s Safe for His Followers to Gather at Protests, Why Doesn’t He Attend One?</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="348"><!-- react-text: 349 -->Robert Mackey<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="350"><!-- react-text: 351 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 352 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="353">Apr. 18</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="354"><!-- react-empty: 355 --></div></div></div></a></div></div><div class="Promo-container" data-reactid="356"><div data-reactid="357"></div><div class="Promo Promo--default Promo--video" data-reactid="358"><a class="Promo-link" href="/2020/04/17/coronavirus-fema-trump-misinformation/" data-reactid="359"><div class="GridRow" data-reactid="360"><div class="Promo-image-container" data-reactid="361"><div class="Promo-image-block" data-reactid="362"><div class="ResponsiveImage Promo-image" style="padding-top:50%;" data-reactid="363"><noscript data-reactid="364"><img src="https://theintercept-static.imgix.net/usq/ad5bd1f0-e9a4-401c-8bcd-e0abe9180a77/ad5bd1f0-e9a4-401c-8bcd-e0abe9180a77.bin?auto=compress,format&cs=srgb&dpr=2&h=450&w=900&fit=crop&crop=faces%2Cedges&_=16a9b30fed6a542d57356b4d399e4727" alt="null" class="ResponsiveImage-image" height="900" width="1800"></noscript></div></div></div><div class="Promo-text" data-reactid="365"><div class="PromoVideoPlayButton Promo-playButton Promo-playButton--in-title" data-reactid="366"></div><div class="Promo-title-block" data-reactid="367"><h4 class="Promo-title" data-reactid="368"><span class="Promo-title-wrap" data-reactid="369">FEMA’s Coronavirus Rumor Control Webpage Sidesteps Trump’s Lies</span></h4><div class="Promo-author" data-reactid="370"><!-- react-text: 371 -->Nick Turse<!-- /react-text --><span class="Promo-date" data-reactid="372"><!-- react-text: 373 --> —<!-- /react-text --><!-- react-text: 374 --> <!-- /react-text --><span data-reactid="375">Apr. 17</span></span></div></div><div class="Promo-excerpt" data-reactid="376"><!-- react-empty: 377 --></div></div></div></a></div></div></div><div class="Post-comments Post-comments-ct" data-reactid="378"><a class="Post-open-comments-link Post-open-comments-link--closed" href="/2018/12/09/brazil-jair-bolsonaro-cabinet/?comments=1#comments" id="comments" data-reactid="379"><span class="Icon Icon--Arrow